  "title": "A man in Brasília-DF reported a cylindrical UFO during a parachuting exhibition [1989]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/10/a-man-in-brasilia-df-reported-a-cilindrical-ufo-during-a-parachuting-exhibition-1989/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1AA",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>APRIL 4th, 1989</strong>. Time: 17:15. Duration: 30 minutes. When he was &#8220;watching a parachuting exhibition&#8221; from the window of his apartment, a man with his family observed an unidentified flying object with a cylindrical shape, silver color and slow speed. According to the reporting witness, the object was about 2,000 meters of altitude, making vertical trajectories of approximately 20 meters. The sighting was carried out with the naked eye and under good observation conditions.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.269. “Questionário sobre ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado no Distrito Federal</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
